      "@id": "https://www.oregonlegislature.gov/bills_laws/ors/ors357.html#section-357.990",
      "identifier": "ORS 357.990",
      "name": "Section 357.990",
      "text": "Penalties. Violation of ORS 357.975 is a Class B violation. Such conviction and payment of the fine shall not be construed to constitute payment for library material nor shall a person convicted under this section be thereby relieved of any obligation to return to the library such material. [Amended by 1971 c.743 360; 1975 c.476 31; 1983 c.208 2; 1999 c.1051 176] _______________",
